==Comparation of Original fortran version and directly translated C++ version==

Step0:
cd directory\of\remap_compare

Step1:
cd ../c++/restore_src
make;./sc2rip > /dev/null;mv *.out ../../remap_compare

Step2:
cd ../fortran
make;.scrip > /dev/null;mv *.scrip ../remap_compare

Step3:
cd ../remap_compare
./run.sh

==--------------------------------------------------------------------------==

==Second C++ version with modification==

cd c++/src

